{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-undefined=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B4%2C0%2C0%2C26%5D%2C%5B4%2C0%2C0%2C26%5D%5D%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><h3 data-lake-id=\"1d89e524067b57cff18962ff2d68691e\" id=\"UAkjq\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px;\">什么是 CSS Houdini ?</h3><p data-lake-id=\"623d8e6284dbb165d5a0bd0cf3c277b7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">CSS Houdini 是由一群來自 Mozilla, Apple, Opera, Microsoft, HP, Intel, IBM, Adobe 与 Google 的工程师所组成的工作小组，建立一系列的 API，让开发者能够介入浏览器的 CSS engine,&nbsp;这些API使开发人员可以直接访问<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\" target=\"_blank\">CSS 对象模型</a>&nbsp;（CSSOM），使开发人员可以编写浏览器可以解析为CSS的代码，从而创建新的CSS功能，而无需等待它们在浏览器中本地实现。</p><p data-lake-id=\"88c3c717aa10e19c9c822df346a17f6e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span>简而言之：CSS Houdini 是一组可以直接访问CSS对象模型的API；</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"62f588841d8bc2e1400a3f6596e5d8e2\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span><br></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"3903d474ac928d74b3f8377eaad7012f\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://css-houdini.rocks/\" target=\"_blank\">https://css-houdini.rocks/</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"d2d5b50c96e5046aa8dbe90db3193aef\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/w3c/css-houdini-drafts\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/w3c/css-houdini-drafts</a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p data-lake-id=\"a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Houdini\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Houdini</a></p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"traditional\" /><h3 data-lake-id=\"1d89e524067b57cff18962ff2d68691e\" id=\"UAkjq\">什么是 CSS Houdini ?</h3><p data-lake-id=\"623d8e6284dbb165d5a0bd0cf3c277b7\">CSS Houdini 是由一群來自 Mozilla, Apple, Opera, Microsoft, HP, Intel, IBM, Adobe 与 Google 的工程师所组成的工作小组，建立一系列的 API，让开发者能够介入浏览器的 CSS engine, 这些API使开发人员可以直接访问<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\" target=\"_blank\">CSS 对象模型</a> （CSSOM），使开发人员可以编写浏览器可以解析为CSS的代码，从而创建新的CSS功能，而无需等待它们在浏览器中本地实现。</p><p data-lake-id=\"88c3c717aa10e19c9c822df346a17f6e\"><span>简而言之：CSS Houdini 是一组可以直接访问CSS对象模型的API；</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"62f588841d8bc2e1400a3f6596e5d8e2\"><span><br /></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"3903d474ac928d74b3f8377eaad7012f\"><a href=\"https://css-houdini.rocks/\" target=\"_blank\">https://css-houdini.rocks/</a></p><p data-lake-id=\"d2d5b50c96e5046aa8dbe90db3193aef\"><a href=\"https://github.com/w3c/css-houdini-drafts\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/w3c/css-houdini-drafts</a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p><p data-lake-id=\"a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Houdini\" target=\"_blank\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/Houdini</a></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-